items.badge_description: Celebrate women and non-binary individuals in craft beer! Every year the Pink Boots Society (PBS) hosts Collaboration Brew Day where teams come together to brew a collab beer that supports the PBS mission to support, inspire, and encourage the professional development of women and non-binary people in the industry. Learn more

There's beer in them thar hills! You're setting off on your journey through the world of beer, but be sure to take a little time to get to know each brewery as you go. That's a beer from 385 different breweries. Try 5 more for Level 78!

Everyone loves fresh beer, but obviously not as much as you do. You went straight to the source. 

That's a beer at 35 different venues categorized as a Brewery, Cidery or Meadery. Visit 5 more for Level 8!
